{"tid":1762796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大鬧英國論壇】掌摑港留學生襲擊罪成 央視女記者判有條件釋放但聲言上訴","createTime":"2019-11-30T00:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T09:34:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6db8c0ad34d7d556b56a3e0a8b4948c755a1bb56","tid":1762796,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:02:17.000Z","msg":"涉嫌在英國保守黨年會一個香港問題論壇上掌摑香港留學生義工的中國央視女記者孔琳琳，被裁定普通襲擊罪名成立，但獲有條件釋放。<br />\n<br />\n在去年9月30日英國保守黨年會座談會上，孔琳琳在場內指罵講者「反華」、「漢奸」和「分裂中國」，被主持人要求離開。她未有遵從指示，聲稱遭四至五人包圍推撞，又指遭擔任會場義工的香港留學生Enoch Lieu的手觸碰。Enoch Lieu否認有用手碰她，只是語調平和地要求她離開。<br />\n法官判案時說，孔琳琳在當時情況下作出兩種反應，首先掌摑Enoch Lieu，跟著把他的手推開。第一項動作明顯是刑事襲擊，第二項則不是。他說：「在的看來，被告在盛怒下失去專業記者的冷靜，變成激烈的質問者。」<br />\n<br />\n法官裁定49歲的孔琳琳罪名成立，判她有條件獲釋12個月，並需支付訟費及賠償100鎊(約1000港元)，共2115鎊(約2.1萬港元)。<br />\n孔琳琳的律師表明她會就判罪和刑期上訴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575052925_1345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575052925_1345.jpg&h=8df68105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575052925_c154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575052925_c154.jpg&h=72002100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191130/60326383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60326383&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY0aSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=a73526b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60326383&h=def27100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191130/60326383</a>"},{"pid":"a2177f8437e537393f432f186e83eb4726074854","tid":1762796,"uid